=== 影响 ===
科尔曾将一些嘻哈艺人列为对其饒舌风格有过影响的，包括[[吐派克·夏庫爾|2Pac]]、[[纳斯|纳斯]]和[[埃米纳姆|埃米纳姆]]。他随后描述[[图派克|图派克]]为他最大的音乐影响<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.hiphopdx.com/index/news/id.15889/title.j-cole-talks-storytelling-working-with-jay-z-kendrick-lamar "J. Cole Talks Storytelling, Working with Jay-Z & Kendrick Lamar"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hiphopdx.com/index/news/id.15889/title.j-cole-talks-storytelling-working-with-jay-z-kendrick-lamar |date=20141126014313 }}. </cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5CvED0F5LAw "J Cole talks Tupac, Jay Z, Eminem & Dreamville | Live with Steve Lobel"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5CvED0F5LAw |date=20201119050108 }}. </cite></ref>。科尔在《Friday Night Lights》发行后被与纳斯间进行对比，而他不久表示，纳斯是这张混音带背后的主要灵感<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.hiphopdx.com/index/news/id.25037/title.nas-j-cole-address-comparisons-to-each-other-lyricism-in-2013 "Nas & J. Cole Address Comparisons To Each Other & Lyricism In 2013"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hiphopdx.com/index/news/id.25037/title.nas-j-cole-address-comparisons-to-each-other-lyricism-in-2013 |date=20150503214721 }}. </cite></ref>。科尔随后在《Let Nas Down》中谈到了他们音乐上的相似之处。这是一首在创作上起因于指向《Work Out》的、针对他的贬损性言论的歌曲<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bLF39513uwM "J. Cole – Let Nas Down (Born Sinner)"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bLF39513uwM |date=20201121023651 }}. </cite></ref>。

== 个人生活 ==
在2016年1月的一次与导演[[瑞安·库格勒|瑞安·库格勒]]的访谈中，瑞安透露出科尔已经结婚的事实<ref><cite class="citation" id="CITEREFMusic-W2016">Music-W (2016-01-18), [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g6fX56ZeIMk ''Put On Blast: Creed Director Ryan Coogler Accidentally Revealed J. Cole Is Married During Interview!''] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g6fX56ZeIMk |date=20170220132214 }}<span class="reference-accessdate">, retrieved <span class="nowrap">2016-04-26</span></span></cite><cite class="citation" id="CITEREFMusic-W2016"></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJ.+Cole&rft.au=Music-W&rft.btitle=Put+On+Blast%3A+Creed+Director+Ryan+Coogler+Accidentally+Revealed+J.+Cole+Is+Married+During+Interview%21&rft.date=2016-01-18&rft.genre=book&rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg6fX56ZeIMk&rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook"> </span></ref>。科尔的妻子、与他有过长期交往的女朋友Melissa Heholt，曾与科尔一道在圣约翰大学就读。她同时也是Dreamville基金会的执行董事长<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://karlawithakay.com/melissa-heholt/ "KWaK chops it up with Melissa Heholt of Statice Events | Celebrating Women's Empowerment | Karla With A Kay"] {{Wayback|url=http://karlawithakay.com/melissa-heholt/ |date=20160420235748 }}. </cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2016/01/j-cole-wife-melissa-heholt/ "Meet J. Cole's New Wife Melissa Heholt - XXL"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2016/01/j-cole-wife-melissa-heholt/ |date=20160506111333 }}. </cite></ref>。

